global blastp_report
blastp_method.metadata = geneseekr.run_blast(metadata=blastp_method.
    metadata, analysistype=blastp_method.analysistype, program=
    blastp_method.program, outfmt=blastp_method.outfmt, evalue=
    blastp_method.evalue, num_threads=blastp_method.cpus)
blastp_report = os.path.join(var.reportpath, 'amr_test_blastp_geneseekr.tsv')
assert os.path.isfile(blastp_report)
